{
  "texts": [
    "Conversely, the group trained with ChatGPT showed a more consistent range of response times, stretching from 2.10 to 6.40 s, and a lower SD of 0.98.",
    "This tighter spread suggests a greater consistency in performance among these participants.",
    "The Mann-Whitney U test was used to ascertain the statistical significance of the differences observed.",
    "The resulting p-value was 0.0002, substantially below the commonly accepted significance level of 0.05.",
    "This indicates that the difference in median activation times between the two groups is statistically significant."
  ]
}